IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GOTO-COMPUTABLE-INSIDE-PERFORM-THROUGH-RANGE.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(20).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY "MAIN BEFORE PERFORM"
PERFORM FIRST THROUGH THIRD
DISPLAY "MAIN AFTER PERFORM"
STOP.

FIRST.
MOVE "THIRD" TO TARGET-FIELD
DISPLAY "FIRST BEFORE COMPUTED GOTO"
GO TO TARGET-FIELD.

SECOND.
DISPLAY "SECOND SHOULD NOT RUN".

THIRD.
DISPLAY "THIRD COMPUTED TARGET".
